So, I started writing this scip last May 14 this year, but didn't end up makng a drafts thread until just this late September cause I was busy at work and had a ton of personal issues.

▶spoilers

◀spoilers


This was originally suppose to be a some sort of soul parasite of the  to humanity due to the Oversoul, where humans being born after 10 billion or 20 billion slowly become deforemd or even anomalous. Anyway, I wasn't really sure how to execute it so I scrapped it immediately.

Months pass, I was doing SEO, and finished my second game, I decided to give this SCP a second try.

This is when I added the  (as Mr. Crayne put it via PM) was a indeed pretty interesting. Although since this was not suppose to be the idea, I struggled to conceptualize further. I had to consult more people and get their feedback and see which works.

Now, either this SCP is about  as suggested by Mr. Crayne.

I pretty much hit bedrock in terms of conceptualizing about this scip so I decided to post it already.

I hope this didn't turn out to be something shit and wasted the effort of people that shaped it.

If you have any ideas or suggestions on how can I further improve this SCP, don't hesitate to comment it down. :)




